+=============================================================+
 MAGENTO EXTENSION BRANDS
+=============================================================+
 
 company:   Attain Design
 author:    Nathan Chick
 version:   0.0.1
 
+=============================================================+
 IMPLEMENTATION
 - Move Files
 - Add a new Attribute called 'brands'
        - Global
        - Drop Down
        - Use in Product Listing
        - Use in Layered Nav
 - Add the Attribute to the Attribute Set
 - Create a table
```SQL
 CREATE TABLE `brands` (
  `brands_id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `name` text,
  `description` text,
  `status` int(1) DEFAULT NULL,
  `attribute_id` int(11) DEFAULT NULL,
  `brandscol` text,
  `file_name` text,
  PRIMARY KEY (`brands_id`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;
```
 
+=============================================================+

 DEPENDANTS
 - WideImage
 - jQuery (Frontend)
 - Attain JS (Frontend)
 - Attain Slider (Frontend)

